Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Spare him some blood! My friend is dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone with blood type S RH negative?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time! Please donate blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.49,Alt,,0,0,0,,We beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sanji-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult for humans\Nto get a blood transfusion on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure Luffy-chin\Nand the others will keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Even though we're searching so hard,\Nwe still can't find anyone who'll donate blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna give up!\NThere has to be somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! I found a human over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This barrel arrived with Camie's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Liquor? Maybe treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but they sure sealid it up tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we open it in secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're well-prepared, Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in town at the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-chin, you've lost most of your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that we found some donors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get up so fast!\NYou need to rest more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But why won't the Fishmen donate blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We looked all over town\Nbut we couldn't find any humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost gave up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, thanks for doing that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was I and what was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can barely remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't think back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.87,Alt,,0,0,0,,No, don't think back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want you to bleed out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Sanji! Let me introduce the blood donors we found at a bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You should thank them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't tell me I got blood\Nfrom such a delicate lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! We're all humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to help each other in times of need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We can give you more, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:37.24,Alt,,0,0,0,,We can give you more, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that he's back to his old self!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you gotta thank them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, let me see your right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A positive reaction to poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! You've been injected with venom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\Nwhen I fought against the Fishmen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt something sting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This poison's really strong.\NAre you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Antibodies must've developed in your body\Nto counter this kind of poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been poisoned before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at Impel Down I almost got poisoned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Poisoned to death?\NThat's nothing to laugh about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The swordsman with the octopus legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He blocked my punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he's pretty strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's coming from the cove.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Mermaids sure are noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are all messed-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I accidentally poisoned Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in trouble if he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishilly and the others were screaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.38,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard them around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard them talking about opening a barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, come here.\NThere's someone I'd like you to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of the Mermaid Café.\NShe let us borrow the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Sharley.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:10.36,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Is the blond boy okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:13.26,Sign,,0,0,365,,{=4}{\blur0.3\fad(750,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(705,750,\1a&H00&)}Owner of the Mermaid Café\NMadame Sharley
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.53,0:10:13.26,Sign,,0,0,365,,{=5}{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(750,0)\4a&HFF&}Owner of the Mermaid Café\NMadame Sharley
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:13.26,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. But since you're such a beautiful lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it's best you stay away from the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And let's not tell Sanji-chin this place\Nis the back room of the Mermaid Café.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,His doctor, Chopper-chin, said that\Nif he finds out, he'll have another attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange prognosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Big Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Madame Sharley, Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch that, Straw Hat boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a crystal ball.\NIt's used for fortune telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame's precognition is famous in Coral Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not practicing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The future is usually best left unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how about this? Do Mermaids poop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do with telling fortunes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Apologize to her, Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.06,Alt,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie, you can take a day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them around the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You always work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,these days we don't have human pirates as guests,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so my business is drying up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls from the cove\Nwill be coming soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have enough\Nstar waitresses to handle customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough star... fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I should have delivered those clams to Pappagu by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so out-of-context!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:12:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Monsieur Pappagu is having fun\Nat the café with an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At the café?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,An old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:06.68,Alt,,0,0,0,,An old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't mention this in front of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but when Madame was a little child,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,she predicted many pirates would start coming to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a year before the Great Pirate Era began.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.57,Alt,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Among a host of other things,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,she recently predicted the war at Marineford
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and Whitebeard's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.66,Alt,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't stand knowing what bad things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's taking care of Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-chin! Usopp-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.72,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the main street of Coral Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! That's the entrance of the Mermaid Café.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm getting hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a {\i1}café{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have food too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cakes and sea fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What about meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We Merfolk don't eat meat or fish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so the menu has things like Kelp Brûlée,\NSeaweed Tart, Kelp Soufflé...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they even edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we have meat too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shellfish meat! Scallop Sandwich, Freshwater Clam Pizza—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shellfish isn't meat!\NHow dare you disrespect meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... Anyway, let's get going!\NTo the Mermaid Café!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Pappagu will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't look down on meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:43.19,Alt,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Resting my bones! Resting my bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you, Bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:08.97,Alt,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Luffy-san and Usopp-san! And it's been a while, Camie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I look at your panti—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw! Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}you{\i0} were with Pappagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I didn't expect to be rescued by Pappagu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was just as much of a surprise for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was trying to perfect an idea\Nfor a new design at the cove,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw some bones\Ndrifting towards me in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Bones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Soul King, come see us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a wonderful time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back, beautiful Mermaids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like they took my backbone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, but if I lose my bones, I'll have nothing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't care if I die today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I'm already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.94,Alt,,0,0,0,,How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He got so worked up over the café...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wonder what's going on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't leaving today, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you are interested in the café
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can come back with everybody later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna take Bones back to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me! Do you like sea monster meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have meat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wild, I don't wanna eat seaweed or shellfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My main food is savage sea monster meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Pappagu, I almost forgot! Here are your clams for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Camie's best clams!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}do{\i0} eat shellfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Mermaids...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fantastic Mermaids...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.77,Alt,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful! Elegant! Wonderful! Sniff, sniff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:32.39,Alt,,0,0,0,,I wonder how they're doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Merfolk, Fishmen eat meat and fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of that kinda food to go around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just what I was looking for! Hey, taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a ghost—why are they looking for him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wasn't this guy on the ghost ship we saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You guys saw him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole nation's been looking for him for years!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a pirate—an undersea bandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about it later. Get on first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Vander Decken was sending love letters\Nto the Mermaid Princess of Ryugu Kingdom every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, the letters became packages,\Nthen threats demanding her hand in marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, it's fluffy! Feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:43.25,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, it's fluffy! Feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's like heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to a starfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.42,Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,His eccentric behavior made the Mermaid Princess\Nafraid and it became of national concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, the Mermaid Princess' father,\NKing Neptune, got mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and those three princes you met earlier mobilized the army to chase after him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but they can't find him anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie, Camie... I was just telling them about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,King Neptune, the God of the Sea,\Nwho runs this country
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,has four children\Nincluding the Mermaid Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mermaid Princess is the youngest and the three princes are older than her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Camie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I can't understand is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Vander Deck must be a ghostly pirate\Nfrom hundreds of years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, those legends are often exaggerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He truly existed and in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the legendary captain, Vander Decken...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,reached Fishman Island and died here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship you saw was\Nthe Flying Dutchman, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his descendant who's on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Vander Decken IX!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! His descendant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That means he's not a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Being only bones, and thinking I'd met a real ghost,\NI was starting to feel more dead than alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie... Camie... Camie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look closer,\NMerfolk and Fishmen are all pretty different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's old Mermaids!\NJust like Grandma Kokoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there's a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The dad's a Fishman, but his children are both Merfolk and Fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When a Mermaid and Fishman get married,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,their kids could be either\NMerfolk or Fishman, boy or girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are four possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm, so that's why they're all different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get on the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a candy factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, why is there a pirate flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That? You can see the same flag\Nat the island's entrance and at the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That flag is protecting Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The mark belongs to a New World pirate called Charlotte Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's also known as Big Mom, one of the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Four Emperors?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the war, the island\Nwas under Whitebeard's protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But nowadays it's Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But she demands a lot of sweet candies\Nevery month in exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the factory is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Candies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This country can't exist\Nwithout the protection of those powerful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how dangerous this place is, where pirates come and go so frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she's protecting the country in old man Whitebeard's place, isn't Big Mom a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard never demanded anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe for Big Mom it's just business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the Four Emperors like Shanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if I'll meet her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in Fishverly Hills, the town of celebs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That tall building right in front of us is Pappagu's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That?! That's way too much for a starfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:43.55,Alt,,0,0,0,,That?! That's way too much for a starfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the Madame from the Mermaid Café.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Madame Sharley?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so distressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do something before it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Madame! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The pirate boy with the straw hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw him out of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a precognition again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't intend to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But something felt off about him
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so I couldn't help looking into the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! What'd you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharley! Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:40.21,Alt,,0,0,0,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be wrong!\NPlease, let my vision be wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A human wearing a straw hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At Straw Hat Luffy's hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.48,0:23:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,at his hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,destroyed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island shines with beauty.\NBut history has shrouded it in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hating humans, they desire retribution.\NThey make their move, deep underneath the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.83,0:23:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Luffy and his crew run amok at Pappagu's shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and the king of Fishman Island,\NNeptune himself, descends from his palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"The King of Fishman Island\NNeptune, the God of the Sea!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.75,0:23:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
